title: 2 bedroom 2 bathroom
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; title: Detached Garages, Gas Range, Covered Parking
neighborhood: 5999 Bear Creek Drive, Bedford Heights, OH
posting_body: ['Columbus Park Apartments provides an affordable selection of Spacious 1, 2, & 3 bedroom apartments tucked away in Bedford Heights, Ohio.', 'Life at Columbus Park Apartments is carefree and convenient.', 'Our landscaped grounds offer plenty of options for you, your family, and your pets to enjoy the fresh air.', 'We offer several convenient parking options such as detached garages and covered parking.', 'We are proud to be one of the few, and best, pet-friendly apartments in the Bedford Heights area.', 'Take your furry friends to our fenced-in Bark Park so they can run around and socialize with other residents.', 'Having a safe and secure playground for your pets is just one of the many convenient amenities we offer.', 'View our full list of apartment amenities and see why our residents love living here.', 'Our community location is set back in a cul-de-sac near Tinker’s Creek.', 'You can also look forward to the many enjoyable attractions that make living at Columbus Park the place to be such as Bedford City School District, close proximity to the Bedford Reservation and Jack Thistledown Racino, as well as several shops and dining in Historic Downtown Bedford.', '-Private Balcony', '-Additional Storage', '-1, 2 & 3 Bedroom Apartments', '-Quiet Cul-De-Sac Location', '-Playground', '-Central Air Conditioning', '-On-Site Management', '-Dishwasher', '-Mini and Vertical Blinds', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-Covered Parking', '-Detached Garages', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday-Friday: 09:00 AM-06:00 PM', 'Saturday: 10:00 AM-03:00 PM', '5999 Bear Creek Drive, Bedford Heights, OH 44146', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

title: Spacious in Walking neighborhood near CCF and UH Hospitals
posting_body: ['Perfect location for living, shopping, and working at the nearby hospitals or Universities.', 'Prime building in a prime location with old world charm found in a brownstone walk-up.', 'Spacious two bedroom suite has hardwood floors throughout with high ceilings.', 'Bath is marble from floor to ceiling.', 'Dining room has charming built-in corner cabinets.', 'Living room has decorative brick fireplace.', 'Eat-in kitchen has nice cabinetry, granite countertops, dishwasher, and disposal.', 'Charming archway between dining and living room provides open floor plan.', 'Ceiling fans in the living room, dining room, and bedroom provide for great circulation.', 'Living room and Dining rooms have great storage closets.', 'New windows for energy efficiency and sound barriers.', 'Conveniently located close to the common laundry facility on-site.', ' Off-street parking available.', 'Located in the Heart of Coventry Village -  a convenient walking neighborhood.', 'Literally a few second walk  to groceries, banks, library, coffee shop (free wi-fi), sports bars, sandwich shops, pizza shop, frozen yogurt parlor, video store, yoga studio, hair salon, drycleaners, bookstore, drug store, music store, nostalgic toy store, hardware store, clothing store, flower shop, sports bar, clubs with live music, 21 restaurants including outdoor dining, and the Peace Park.', 'Close to the Cleveland Clinic Foundation, Lerner College of Medicine, Case Medical School,  Case Dental School, Huron Road Hospital, VA Hospital, Metro General Hospital, Hillcrest Hospital, Ahuja Hospital and University Hospital.', ' On the loop of Case Western Reserve University, near Case Law School, Cleveland State University, and John Carroll University.', 'Call 216 536-64O5 (no random texts, please) for more information or to schedule an appointment.', 'If replying to this ad via email, please provide your name and phone number.', ' Thank you']

title: Disposal, Rentable Surface Lot, High Ceilings
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High are centrally located in the heart of one of Cleveland's historic neighborhoods.", 'Let your home reflect your passion for design with a story.', 'See yourself in our Cudell Cleveland apartments.', '-Dishwasher', '-Public Transportation', '-Wheelchair Access', '-Rhino Security Deposit Option', '-Rentable Garage', '-Elevator', '-On-Site Management', '-BBQ/Picnic Area', '-Recreation Room', '-Disposal', '-Package Lockers', '-High Ceilings', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday: 9AM-6PM', 'Tuesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Wednesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Thursday: 9AM-6PM', 'Friday: 10AM-3PM', '2201 W. 93rd Street, Cleveland, OH 44102', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

title: 3 bedroom 2 bathroom
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; title: High Ceilings, BBQ/Picnic Area, Wheelchair Access
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High are centrally located in the heart of one of Cleveland's historic neighborhoods.", 'Let your home reflect your passion for design with a story.', 'See yourself in our Cudell Cleveland apartments.', '-Refrigerator', '-On-Site Management', '-W/D Hookup', '-Electronic Thermostat', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-Laundry Facilities', '-Package Lockers', '-Elevator', '-Rentable Surface Lot', '-Rentable Garage', '-Large Closets', '-Historic Building', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday: 9AM-6PM', 'Tuesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Wednesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Thursday: 9AM-6PM', 'Friday: 10AM-3PM', '2201 W. 93rd Street, Cleveland, OH 44102', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

title: Single Family Home w/Basement, Laundry, Closets, Backyard! (Cl
posting_body: ['Welcome to 13509 Courtland Avenue, a beautiful and delightful three-bedroom home that has been properly kept and cared for over the years.', 'Courtland Ave.', 'You are welcomed into the spacious living room with newer carpet as soon as you walk through the front entrance with stained glass panels.', 'From there, you can access the spacious eat-in kitchen, which has formica counters, white oak cabinets, and a ceramic tile backsplash.', 'This room has a wonderful view of the lovely backyard.', 'On the main floor, there are two roomy bedrooms with hardwood floors, a modern full bathroom with ceramic tile flooring, and a practical tub/shower combo.', 'The entire second level is devoted to the roomy Primary Bedroom, which has wood paneled walls and modern carpet.', 'On the second floor, there is a lot of closet and storage space available, including built-in shelving and an enormous cedar closet to suit your needs.', 'The partially finished basement provides more living space as well as a big activity room with updated flooring and glass block windows for your enjoyment.', 'The lower level also has a partial bathroom.', 'In addition, this house has a great backyard that is completely enclosed by fencing, a detached 1-car garage, and extra storage space.', "It is close to the Kamm's Corners area and has easy access to both the Metroparks and the Interstate.", "Simple commute to Cleveland's downtown and beyond.", "Don't pass up the chance to see everything that this unique home has to offer!"]

title: Dynamic yet cozy, 2 Bed 2 Bath, Ready for move in, in 2 weeks!
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High are centrally located in the heart of one of Cleveland's historic neighborhoods.", 'Let your home reflect your passion for design with a story.', 'See yourself in our Cudell Cleveland apartments.', '-Microwave', '-High Ceilings', '-Elevator', '-On-Site Management', '-Short Term Lease', '-Electronic Thermostat', '-Wheelchair Access', '-W/D Hookup', '-Dishwasher', '-Rentable Surface Lot', '-Cable Ready', '-Carpeting', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday: 9AM-6PM', 'Tuesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Wednesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Thursday: 9AM-6PM', 'Friday: 10AM-3PM', '2201 W. 93rd Street, Cleveland, OH 44102', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

posting_body: ['Come check out this gorgeous single-family home that was rehabbed in 2018 right near Gordon Square.', 'This home has an open floor plan on the first floor with living room, dining room, a giant kitchen, half bath, and mud room.', 'The second floor has 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and laundry.', 'The third floor can be used as a 3rd bedroom or office and living space.', 'The back yard is fenced-in and has a 2-car attached garage.', 'The front of the house has a large front porch that is great for sitting out on warm summer days.', 'This house is a very short walk from the Gordon Square Arts District, Edgewater Park, and new bike trails.', "Come check out this house to live in one of Cleveland's hottest areas!", 'Open to shorter-term leases and can negotiate option of partial or fully-furnished.', 'Email or text to set up a showing.']

posting_body: ['Nicely 2 bedroom 2 bathroom apartment in the heart of the Cleveland .Offering an unexpected abundance of outdoor space, this home is fronted by a large shared patio, and topped with a third-floor wrap-around deck leading to a show-stopper of a roof-top terrace, with built-in planters, an irrigation system, and sweeping views of the Center City skyline and Yuma Landing.', 'off street parking.', 'backyard area.', 'Central Air.', 'Great neighborhood.', 'Cats ok Dogs with landlord approval.', 'You would share the kitchen and family room with the other two tenants.', 'The house has a small but complete kitchen, a "family room" no tv, an indoor washer/dryer, and 1 parking space per tenant.', 'It is in a lovely quiet neighborhood.', 'Although the house.', "If you are looking for a comfortable place, with nice and considerate people that you won't see much of, this might be the place you are looking for.", 'Smoke free, pet free environment.', 'The neighbor has chickens that are rather loud in the morning and can definitely be heard from your room.', 'Recently renovated apartment.', 'Great location and close to FLC, trolley stops and downtown.', 'Upper-level unit in a small complex with off-street parking.', 'No smoking/pets.', 'Rent includes water, sewer, trash and recycling.', '$745 per month.', 'Off street parking.', 'Large shared yard space.', 'Utilities, lawn maintenance and snow removal are responsibility of tenant.', 'The neighbor has chickens that are rather loud in the morning and can definitely be heard from your room.', 'Text me if interested.', 'Thank you']

title: 3 Bed 2 Bath, 2 Story Loft Apartment Move in ready by 7/25/2022
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High are centrally located in the heart of one of Cleveland's historic neighborhoods.", 'Let your home reflect your passion for design with a story.', 'See yourself in our Cudell Cleveland apartments.', '-BBQ/Picnic Area', '-W/D Hookup', '-Microwave', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-Laundry Facilities', '-Recreation Room', '-Short Term Lease', '-Large Closets', '-Carpeting', '-Rhino Security Deposit Option', '-Rentable Garage', '-Elevator', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday: 9AM-6PM', 'Tuesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Wednesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Thursday: 9AM-6PM', 'Friday: 10AM-3PM', '2201 W. 93rd Street, Cleveland, OH 44102', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High are centrally located in the heart of one of Cleveland's historic neighborhoods.", 'Let your home reflect your passion for design with a story.', 'See yourself in our Cudell Cleveland apartments.', '-Short Term Lease', '-Rentable Garage', '-Refrigerator', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-Recreation Room', '-BBQ/Picnic Area', '-Disposal', '-Cable Ready', '-Wheelchair Access', '-Public Transportation', '-Courtyard', '-High Ceilings', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday: 9AM-6PM', 'Tuesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Wednesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Thursday: 9AM-6PM', 'Friday: 10AM-3PM', '2201 W. 93rd Street, Cleveland, OH 44102', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

title: LOOKING FOR ROOMIES FOR 3 BED 3 BATH HOUSE
posting_body: ['*READ BEFORE MESSAGING*', '**SERIOUS INQUIRES ONLY**', 'Looking for new CLEAN, QUIET and RESPONSIBLE housemates for this two-story beautiful house.', 'Current housemates are leaving in august or september when the lease ends!', 'I will need to sign a new lease, for another year.', 'A little about me:', 'I work at In n out, planning on getting a second job', 'so I’ll be busy.', 'I have a 3 year old dog, she’s sweet, quiet and friendly, half chihuahua/rottweiler.', 'About the place:', 'I have three bedrooms freeing up august or September for $1100 each all of which are unfurnished.', 'I will need proof of income.', 'This does not include utilities which are another $50-70 a month.', 'I will need a deposit of 500 before you move in.', 'Couples/roommates are welcomed to share the room if you’d like.', 'You’ll be sharing the bathroom with two other roommates.', 'There’s an in unit washer and dryer.', 'Location:', 'Great location, it’s located by high school, Target, Evergreen, Costco business center ect.', 'I can’t really show off the rooms since the housemates are still living here and because of privacy.', 'But I can show u the house, the kitchen and living room and backyard so we could meet in person.', 'There’s plenty of street parking.', 'If i am not able to find housemates by augusr or September 1st will be moving out.', 'If you see this post up this is still available.', 'Thank you!', 'Message me for more info and an introduction of yourself!']

title: Detached Garages, On-Site Laundry Facilities, Dishwasher
neighborhood: 5999 Bear Creek Drive, Bedford Heights, OH
posting_body: ['Columbus Park Apartments provides an affordable selection of Spacious 1, 2, & 3 bedroom apartments tucked away in Bedford Heights, Ohio.', 'Life at Columbus Park Apartments is carefree and convenient.', 'Our landscaped grounds offer plenty of options for you, your family, and your pets to enjoy the fresh air.', 'We offer several convenient parking options such as detached garages and covered parking.', 'We are proud to be one of the few, and best, pet-friendly apartments in the Bedford Heights area.', 'Take your furry friends to our fenced-in Bark Park so they can run around and socialize with other residents.', 'Having a safe and secure playground for your pets is just one of the many convenient amenities we offer.', 'View our full list of apartment amenities and see why our residents love living here.', 'Our community location is set back in a cul-de-sac near Tinker’s Creek.', 'You can also look forward to the many enjoyable attractions that make living at Columbus Park the place to be such as Bedford City School District, close proximity to the Bedford Reservation and Jack Thistledown Racino, as well as several shops and dining in Historic Downtown Bedford.', '-Wooded Surroundings', '-Refrigerator', '-Central Air Conditioning', '-Private Balcony', '-Online Rental Payments', '-Dishwasher', '-Mini and Vertical Blinds', '-Quiet Cul-De-Sac Location', '-On-Site Management', '-Gas Range', '-Detached Garages', '-On-Site Laundry Facilities', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday-Friday: 09:00 AM-06:00 PM', 'Saturday: 10:00 AM-03:00 PM', '5999 Bear Creek Drive, Bedford Heights, OH 44146', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

title: Rare! 2-bed up unit in desirable Westpark w/parking; Avail 9/1
map_address: 3277 Rocky River Dr. near Edgecliff & Munn Avenues
posting_body: ['Gorgeous upstairs, second-floor unit of a high-quality, 2-family home.', 'Professionally updated and recently remodeled!', 'Beautifully maintained.', 'Hardwood floors in kitchen, dining, and living rooms.', 'Clean carpeting in the rest of the apartment with newer windows and a solid brick exterior.', 'Two bedrooms plus one extra bonus room (office, study, den, TV/reading room, playroom) off the second bedroom.', 'Living room, dining room, eat-in kitchen, one bathroom.', 'Kitchen appliances stay, including a new dishwasher and disposal, plus a built-in wine rack.', 'New Nest thermostat.', 'Loads of storage.', 'Your own newer, non-shared washer and dryer in the basement with room for extra storage.', 'Deep manicured back yard with large deck.', 'New driveway.', 'Detached garage with electric door opener and parking for 1 spot.', "Wonderful location in highly desirable West Park neighborhood near Kamm's Shopping Plaza, Fairview Hospital, schools (Our Lady of Angels, St. Joseph's Academy, St. Mark's), airport, I-90, Lakewood, Rocky River, and Metroparks.", 'Also close to several churches and libraries.', 'Tenant responsible for all utilities, including water and sewer.', 'ABSOLUTELY NO PETS (only exception: service animal).', 'NO SMOKING.', 'Sorry, no Section 8 vouchers.', 'Minimum credit score: 675.', 'Subject to background check.', "First month's rent, last month's rent, and security deposit all due upon signing.", 'Tours by appointment only.', 'Available Sept. 1, 2022!']

title: Cozy 2 Bed, 2 Bath
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; title: 2 Bedroom 2 Bathroom
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High are centrally located in the heart of one of Cleveland's historic neighborhoods.", 'Let your home reflect your passion for design with a story.', 'See yourself in our Cudell Cleveland apartments.', '-Laundry Facilities', '-Ceiling Fan', '-BBQ/Picnic Area', '-Short Term Lease', '-High Ceilings', '-Refrigerator', '-Recreation Room', '-Cable Ready', '-Disposal', '-Carpeting', '-Dishwasher', '-Fitness Center', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday: 9AM-6PM', 'Tuesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Wednesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Thursday: 9AM-6PM', 'Friday: 10AM-3PM', '2201 W. 93rd Street, Cleveland, OH 44102', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

posting_body: ['LOCATION MATTERS!', 'UNIQUE LAKEFRONT RENTAL!', 'Enjoy this airy beauty with the beach at your doorstep and panoramic lake views.', 'Private association beach is shallow, sandy, family-friendly.', 'Open floor plan, tons of light, windows and lake breezes.', 'Walk to the Vermilion Country Club to golf and the local convenience store for those last-minute beverages or grilling essentials.', 'Gas grill, washer and dryer, bedding, towels, microwave, flatware and dishes all included.', 'Two bedrooms: main bdrm w queen bed, guest bedroom sleeps three to four w double bed bottom bunk and single (twin) upper.', "Minutes from Historic downtown Vermilion, Cedar Point, Sawmill Creek, local access to PutnBay, Kelly's Island and local wineries.", 'Great location for family gatherings or business travelers alike.', 'Please email dates of stay, number of guests as well as reason for stay to Suzie.', 'Available for month to month rental.']

title: Dishwasher, Wooded Surroundings, On-Site Laundry Facilities
neighborhood: 5999 Bear Creek Drive, Bedford Heights, OH
posting_body: ['Columbus Park Apartments provides an affordable selection of Spacious 1, 2, & 3 bedroom apartments tucked away in Bedford Heights, Ohio.', 'Life at Columbus Park Apartments is carefree and convenient.', 'Our landscaped grounds offer plenty of options for you, your family, and your pets to enjoy the fresh air.', 'We offer several convenient parking options such as detached garages and covered parking.', 'We are proud to be one of the few, and best, pet-friendly apartments in the Bedford Heights area.', 'Take your furry friends to our fenced-in Bark Park so they can run around and socialize with other residents.', 'Having a safe and secure playground for your pets is just one of the many convenient amenities we offer.', 'View our full list of apartment amenities and see why our residents love living here.', 'Our community location is set back in a cul-de-sac near Tinker’s Creek.', 'You can also look forward to the many enjoyable attractions that make living at Columbus Park the place to be such as Bedford City School District, close proximity to the Bedford Reservation and Jack Thistledown Racino, as well as several shops and dining in Historic Downtown Bedford.', '-Mini and Vertical Blinds', '-Covered Parking', '-Quiet Cul-De-Sac Location', '-Playground', '-Online Rental Payments', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-Additional Storage', '-Gas Range', '-Wooded Surroundings', '-Dishwasher', '-Detached Garages', '-1, 2 & 3 Bedroom Apartments', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday-Friday: 09:00 AM-06:00 PM', 'Saturday: 10:00 AM-03:00 PM', '5999 Bear Creek Drive, Bedford Heights, OH 44146', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

title: 2 bed, 2 bath, large living area
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High are centrally located in the heart of one of Cleveland's historic neighborhoods.", 'Let your home reflect your passion for design with a story.', 'See yourself in our Cudell Cleveland apartments.', '-Wheelchair Access', '-Recreation Room', '-Electronic Thermostat', '-High Ceilings', '-Refrigerator', '-Laundry Facilities', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-Rentable Garage', '-Fitness Center', '-Disposal', '-BBQ/Picnic Area', '-Elevator', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday: 9AM-6PM', 'Tuesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Wednesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Thursday: 9AM-6PM', 'Friday: 10AM-3PM', '2201 W. 93rd Street, Cleveland, OH 44102', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

posting_body: ['Welcome to the popular Coventry Village Neighborhood.', 'Prime building in a prime location with old world charm found in a brownstone walk-up.', 'Spacious two bedroom suite has hardwood floors throughout with high ceilings.', 'Bath is marble from floor to ceiling.', 'Dining room has charming built-in corner cabinets.', 'Living room has decorative brick fireplace.', 'Eat-in kitchen has nice cabinetry, granite countertops, dishwasher, and disposal.', 'Charming archway between dining and living room provides open floor plan.', 'Ceiling fans in the living room, dining room, and bedroom provide for great circulation.', 'Living room and Dining rooms have great storage closets.', 'New windows for energy efficiency and sound barriers.', 'Conveniently located close to the common laundry facility on-site.', ' Off-street parking available.', 'Located in the Heart of Coventry Village -  a convenient walking neighborhood.', 'Literally a few second walk  to groceries, banks, library, coffee shop (free wi-fi), sports bars, sandwich shops, pizza shop, frozen yogurt parlor, video store, yoga studio, hair salon, drycleaners, bookstore, drug store, music store, nostalgic toy store, hardware store, clothing store, flower shop, sports bar, clubs with live music, 21 restaurants including outdoor dining, and the Peace Park.', 'Close to the Cleveland Clinic Foundation, Lerner College of Medicine, Case Medical School,  Case Dental School, Huron Road Hospital, VA Hospital, Metro General Hospital, Hillcrest Hospital, Ahuja Hospital and University Hospital.', ' On the loop of Case Western Reserve University, near Case Law School, Cleveland State University, and John Carroll University.', 'Call 216 536-64O5 (no random texts, please) for more information or to schedule an appointment.', 'If replying to this ad via email, please provide your name and phone number.', ' Thank you']

title: 2 Bed, 2 Bath, 2 Level Loft
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; posting_body: ['This Spacious two bedroom, two full bath apartment in Shaker Square (Shaker School District) is newly renovated.', 'It has carpet, large closets and includes all appliances.', ' You will love the convenience of on-site laundry facilities and free outdoor parking.', ' Enclosed parking available for an additional fee.', ' The apartment is located on the bus line and is within walking distance to the Rapid, restaurants, grocery store and retail shops.', ' Enjoy the Farmers Market, Summer entertainment, Christmas lighting and other seasonal activities at Shaker Square.', ' Garage space is $30 per month.', 'Located close to University Circle, Hospitals, Cleveland Clinic.', 'This building has a no smoking policy.', 'It is a smoke-free property, meaning that anyone found to be smoking in the building is faced with the loss of their security deposit and possible eviction.', 'Requirements:', 'FICO scores 670+ require a security deposit same as one month rent, stable employment, proof of income, favorable rental history, no criminal record in the past ten years,  and no evictions within last five years.', 'Scores 640 to 669 require a double security deposit.', 'Scores 600 to 639 require a double security deposit and a co-signer with a FICO credit score of over 700.', 'No Section 8.', 'No pets allowed.', 'How to contact us:', '- Please send your FICO credit score, the type of business, your cell number, and any questions to this email address.', '- Please first respond by email and then also call', 'show contact info', 'and leave a message.', '- If you do not get respond within 48 hours, please, then, first text (only) Carole at 2216-538-0813; and finally contact text (only)', 'Renee at', 'show contact info', '.']

title: Want Affordable Living Downtown? ALL Utilities Included!!
posting_body: ["Stockbridge Apartments offers Effeciencies, Studio's , 1 bedroom and 2 bedroom suites.", 'Live in the Historical Landmark, Stockbridge Hotel', 'The Stockbridge Apartments in Cleveland, Ohio offers a variety of floor plans and amenities that meet a wide range of tastes and needs.', 'You can live in this beautiful Historical Landmark today!', 'As a former hotel built on Euclid Avenue\'s famous "Millionaire\'s Row", our apartment homes feature classic and elegant designs with many original details preserved.', 'The apartment amenities range from Carpet, Ceiling Fans, Controlled Access, Hardwood Floor, Balconies with select suites, Cats Allowed, Tile Floors, Walk In Closets, a well equipped laundry room and more!', 'We are located on the border of Downtown & Midtown District in Cleveland - within walking distance of Cleveland State University and a short drive to many area employers.', 'Located on the Health Line (Euclid Corridor), Minutes away from EVERY downtown convenience.', 'You will fall in love with your new home.', 'As an NM Residential resident you can look forward to:', '• 24 hour emergency maintenance', '• Well trained, professional staff', '• Easy, online maintenance request', '• Convenient online payments available', 'In addition, Stockbridge Apartments will offer you:', 'ALL utilities included.', 'Gated Parking', 'Covered Parking', 'Laundry Facility', 'Walking distance to the Euclid Health Line bus service.', 'I-90 and the Health Line put downtown conveniences just minutes away.', 'To schedule your personalized tour today, please contact us at', 'show contact info', '.', 'You can also visit us online at <URL> for additional photos and floorplans.']

title: 3 Bed 2 Bath Penthouse Loft, Apply today, move in tomorrow!
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; title: 2BR Apartment With Loads of Charm!
map_address: 184 South State Street near East South Street
posting_body: ['Welcome to your new spacious 2 bedroom/1 bath apartment.', "You say you really don't need a 2nd bedroom?", 'Well this is a great price for this 1000 square foot apartment.', ' ', 'And you have so many options for the "2nd" bedroom here - you can of course use it as a bedroom', 'OR you can use it as an office, library, craft room, game room or walk-in closet!', 'You also have a full size, eat-in kitchen, a full bathroom, high ceilings, great size bedrooms and closets and a living room with plenty of natural sunlight.', 'There is attic storage as an added bonus too!', 'You have your own entrance off of the large, shared front porch that leads to the beautiful wood staircase that takes you up to your apartment.', 'The spare bedroom and full bath are off of the hallway when you enter and your large, full kitchen and living room are on the other side.', ' The master bedroom is located conveniently off of the living room and the large windows throughout the apartment let in plenty of light.', 'Your rent includes trash removal and you are responsible for the heat, electric, water and sewer.', 'We do also have a parking lot for our residents (guests have street parking).', 'We do allow up to 2 pet cats OR one small pet dog (no larger than 25 lbs full grown) at list property - however additional fees apply.', 'This apartment WILL NOT last!', 'If you are interested, just go directly to our website, review our Criteria/Rules and Regulations, watch the virtual tour and apply right online.', 'If you have additional questions, please feel free to contact our office.', 'PYA Management Group', 'show contact info', '<URL>']

title: 2 story Brick live/work residence - available furnished
posting_body: ['A beautiful mixed use building converted into a 2 story residence is now available for rent in the Lorain Avenue Arts District.', 'This is a truly unique live/work opportunity for young professionals who work from home, roommates seeking a truly urban experience in this home converted from an antique shop, or a great alternative for a couple with a dog looking to rent a single family home with a dog park in the backyard!', ' Each floor has a 1000 sq.', 'ft. footprint with hardwood floors throughout and tons of daylight with a double storefront and off street parking!', "The first floor is one large open space with 11' ceilings, exposed brick, a pair of elevated southern facing display windows, set up as a living room and guest suite.", 'The storefront features new industrial lighting, and two layers of drapes for varying levels of privacy to suite your needs.', 'Inside the ceiling and walls are painted matte white with vintage crystal chandeliers, original painted tin moldings, maple hardwood floors, and plenty of daylight coming in through privacy windows on the east and west.', 'There is a small storage area, as well as a kitchenette including a full size french-door refrigerator on the first floor; in the basement is full bath with a clawfoot tub, understair storage, and access to a washer, dryer.', "There is a 9' tall garage door that opens up to the rear yard, as well as a cedar clad doghouse.", 'The fully fenced-in yard was landscaped with river rock throughout for parking; it is also great for entertaining as it includes a fire pit and bar height table for entertaining guests.', "The second floor has 9' ceilings and is a beautifully restored 1 bedroom/1 bath flat.", 'It features new hardwood floors in all living spaces, new subway tile in the bathroom, granite countertops and stainless appliances in the kitchen, beautiful woodwork, a brick mantle, new energy efficient windows with new paint throughout.', 'The layout is wide open with a huge kitchen, tons of natural light, and plenty of closet space.', 'It is located in the infamous antique district of Historic Lorain Avenue, next to a number of shops.', 'It is only a 5 minute walk to the western entrance of the new Red Line Greenway multi-purpose trail, the RTA tram station, and Zone Park.', 'It is a 5 minute bike ride to Ohio City on the recently repaved Avenue.', 'It is situated halfway between West Boulevard and West 65th and adjacent to I-90 for quick vehicular access wherever you want to go; within 5 minutes by car, you also can get to the heart of Detroit Shoreway, Edgewater Beach, or Downtown Cleveland.', 'The rehab of this completely brick building from 1905 earned a historic renovation award from the Detroit Shoreway Community Development Corporation.', 'It is truly a diamond in the rough and is equipped with a security system, motion lights, and surveillance.', 'This 2 bedroom / 2 Bath / 2 Story Brick Home is available for rent strictly for residential use at $1750.00/month plus utilities (gas, electricity, water) on a one year lease.', 'Cats or dogs are welcome with a pet deposit, at $50.00/pet/month.', 'If you are interested in the place already furnished as shown, the place is setup for you to move right in.', 'Downstairs includes a king bed, end tables, love seat, area rugs, a 42 inch LCD TV, a sound system, projector, lockers, a desk and kitchenette.', 'The flat upstairs has a new full sized 12 inch mattress with a memory foam topper on a platform frame, an extra wardrobe, and a 40 inch Smart LED TV.', 'It also includes plenty of chairs, a loveseat, a maple dining room table, and a desk.', ' If you would like the apartment furnished, this is an option for an additional $200/month.', "To set up a showing of this one-of-a-kind place with our property manager, please send an email introducing yourself, what interests you about this property, and anything else you wish to share; employment verification, prior landlord references, credit check and proof of 100K in renter's insurance are required on your application.", "A signed lease will include a security deposit equal to the month's rent, with digital rent transfers set up on an automated monthly basis.", 'Please be in touch with interest, inquiries, or a request to check out the property.', 'Our property manager will be in touch.', 'Thank you very much!']

posting_body: ['Columbus Park Apartments provides an affordable selection of Spacious 1, 2, & 3 bedroom apartments tucked away in Bedford Heights, Ohio.', 'Life at Columbus Park Apartments is carefree and convenient.', 'Our landscaped grounds offer plenty of options for you, your family, and your pets to enjoy the fresh air.', 'We offer several convenient parking options such as detached garages and covered parking.', 'We are proud to be one of the few, and best, pet-friendly apartments in the Bedford Heights area.', 'Take your furry friends to our fenced-in Bark Park so they can run around and socialize with other residents.', 'Having a safe and secure playground for your pets is just one of the many convenient amenities we offer.', 'View our full list of apartment amenities and see why our residents love living here.', 'Our community location is set back in a cul-de-sac near Tinker’s Creek.', 'You can also look forward to the many enjoyable attractions that make living at Columbus Park the place to be such as Bedford City School District, close proximity to the Bedford Reservation and Jack Thistledown Racino, as well as several shops and dining in Historic Downtown Bedford.', '-Gas Range', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-Covered Parking', '-Detached Garages', '-Wooded Surroundings', '-Fenced-In Dog Park', '-On-Site Laundry Facilities', '-Quiet Cul-De-Sac Location', '-On-Site Management', '-Playground', '-Additional Storage', '-Refrigerator', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday-Friday: 09:00 AM-06:00 PM', 'Saturday: 10:00 AM-03:00 PM', '5999 Bear Creek Drive, Bedford Heights, OH 44146', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

title: 18771 State Rd
posting_body: ['Beautiful Ranch style brick home set on a nice lot.', 'This home has many unique features.', 'There is a spacious living room and dining area at the front entrance with wooded floors throughout the home.', 'The three bedrooms are located on the first floor.', 'Updated, modern bathroom.', 'Kitchen has built in stove, range top, dishwasher and a built-in kitchen table.', 'Attached one car garage (back garage is not accessible for tenant use).', 'The basement is set up for entertaining with a working wood fireplace along with a gas heater and a pool table for tenant use.', 'The back room has a large area for storage, laundry hook-ups and an additional shower.', 'The home has the option to have first floor laundry or to utilize hook-ups in the basement.', 'Enjoy the wooded view from either the heated three season room or the back deck.', 'Lawn is maintained by the owner.', 'Please use the driveway to turn around, DO NOT BACK OUT!', 'Property will be professionally managed, all interested applicants can apply online or contact the agent.', 'There is a $50 application fee per each adult.', 'Vouchers are not accepted for this property.', 'No smoking, no pets.']

street_address: 1823 Lee Road, Cain Park, Cleveland Heights, OH
app_fee: Application fee is $30 for one and $50 for two people
posting_body: ["Welcome to Cain Park apartments, conveniently located near University Circle and the area's top hospitals and colleges/universities.", ' Many new High Resolution Security Cameras protect all parking lots , driveways, staircases ,  hallways and doors.', ' This large two bedroom is freshly painted and renovated.', 'It offers two walk-in closets, refrigerator, range, dishwasher and a central air condition unit.', ' The building has an elevator, on-site laundry facilities and free outdoor parking.', ' Enclosed parking is available for an additional fee.', 'Rent includes heat, water, sewer and trash pick up.', 'The building is conveniently located on a bus line and within walking distance to restaurants, grocery stores, other retail shops and Cain Park.', 'It is close to University Circle, Cleveland Clinic and University Hospital.', 'No pets allowed.', 'This building has a no smoking policy.', 'It is a smoke-free property, meaning that anyone found to be smoking in the building is faced with the loss of their security deposit and possible eviction.', 'No Section 8.', 'Six month leases are available, but come with additional rent and additional conditions.', 'Rent starts at $845.', 'Requirements:', 'FICO scores 670+ require a security deposit same as one month rent, stable employment, proof of income, favorable rental history, no criminal record in the past ten years,  and no evictions within last five years.', 'Scores 640 to 669 require a double security deposit.', 'Scores 600 to 639 require a double security deposit and a co-signer with a FICO credit score of over 700.', 'No Section 8.', 'No pets allowed.', 'How to contact us:', '- Please send your FICO credit score, the type of business, your cell number, and any questions to this email address.', '- Please first respond by email and then also call', 'show contact info', 'and leave a message.', '- If you do not get respond within 48 hours, please, then, first text (only) Carole at 2216-538-0813; and finally contact text (only)', 'Renee at', 'show contact info', '.', 'update 7.4.22']

title: 3 Bedroom, 3 Bathroom townhouse w/jacuzzi tub!
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; title: Cable Ready, Electronic Thermostat, On-Site Management
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High are centrally located in the heart of one of Cleveland's historic neighborhoods.", 'Let your home reflect your passion for design with a story.', 'See yourself in our Cudell Cleveland apartments.', '-W/D Hookup', '-Carpeting', '-Ceiling Fan', '-Elevator', '-Wheelchair Access', '-Rentable Garage', '-Historic Building', '-Refrigerator', '-Microwave', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-Recreation Room', '-Rhino Security Deposit Option', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday: 9AM-6PM', 'Tuesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Wednesday: 9AM-6PM', 'Thursday: 9AM-6PM', 'Friday: 10AM-3PM', '2201 W. 93rd Street, Cleveland, OH 44102', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

title: Why Rent When You Can BUY!!
posting_body: ["Many renters think they don't have enough money to buy a house, when in reality if you are paying around $800 a month for rent, then you may be able to qualify for a mortgage and buy a home!", 'Owning a home has so many benefits, one of them being your monthly payment goes towards something valuable and you gain equity in your home.', "When you are renting, your money isn't benefiting you at all, it is just making your landlord richer.", 'If you are considering purchasing a home, feel free to contact me and I would be glad to help and walk you through the process.', 'Bryan Toro,', 'Realtor, Keller Williams Citywide', 'Hablo Espanol']

title: Check out this wonderful updated home ready for move in ASAP
posting_body: ['Check out this wonderful updated home new carpet and vinyl windows full basement with washer and dryer hook up with new pex plumbing.', ' Large kitchen, leading to full dinning room and large living room.', ' 3 full bedrooms and full bath on second floor.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '..', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '.', '..', '.', '.', '..', '.', '.', '.', 'My apartment is being renovated and therefore uninhabitable for most of September', "so I'll need a short-term living situation until the work is finished.", "I can't give exact dates until the work starts, but I'll need housing starting Labor Day and going for about a month.", "I'm not very particular and my only basic requirements are a place where I can get a peaceful night's sleep, has a comfortable bed (if the place is unfurnished, I could bring a bed with me), a place to stash my bike, and (if it's an apartment with roommates) co-habitants with whom I can get along.", "I don't need a beautiful apartment or a room with a view; I work a lot and just need a place to unwind in the evening and sleep for the night.", "I won't have much stuff with me because I'll be able to get things from my apartment as needed, so I would only have a few personal items and my clothes for the week.", "I've had roommates in the past (it's been a while, but I'm an agreeable fellow).", "I'm pretty social and will go with the vibe of the living situation.", 'I might want to crack open a beer and watch a movie with you and I might want to get some work done in private and pass out.', "I'm supportive of the LGBTQ+ community and welcome living with people who identify as such.", "I'm in my early 40s, teach in a NYC public school, enjoy cooking and can make enough to share, and will pretty much stay out of your way.", "I always work long hours, and the start of the school year always keeps me especially late, plus I'll supervise student activities most afternoons.", "I'll probably leave town each weekend and take most or all of my things with me until I get back to start the workweek.", "I highly doubt I'll have any visitors.", "Please let me know about the apartment, how long you can make the living space available, who might be living there while I'd be there, and anything else you think I might need to know.", "I'm cool with pets.", 'How payment and security will work.', 'What you need from me.', 'Those sorts of things.', "Whenever I had looked for long-term living situations in the past, I'd been pretty discerning and sought the perfect situation.", "This time around I'm just looking for a situation that's functional", 'Seeking a clean in-law apartment or private room in September timeframe for a weekly rental, preferably just south of Boston but all good rooms will be considered.', "I am the dream tenant you've been seeking - responsible, quiet, mature full-time working professional .", 'Clean, non-smoker, non drug-user, excellent credit, no pets.', 'I spend many weekends away from the greater Boston area.', 'Seeking a room in a non-smoking location with private bath and preferably a private entrance, possibly a kitchenette.', 'Seeking off-street parking.', 'Week to week or month to month rental or short term lease preferred.', 'Please me if you have something available or coming available.', 'When responding, please describe what you have for rent: location (city/town), rent $$, private bath or entrance, size of room., etc.', 'Rent negotiable based on amenities.', 'I am not seeking a high cost whole apartment.', 'Thank you.', 'Arlington, Bedford, Belmont, Burlington, Cambridge, Lexington, Lincoln, Medford, Newton, Somerville, Waltham, Watertown, Weston, Winchester, Woburn.', 'Other locations considered.', 'do NOT me with unsolicited services or offers', "I've been very happy living with my current roommate in a one bedroom apartment for the few years.", 'I converted the spacious walk in closet into a private room I use to sleep and chill in after work.', 'This might sound strange to some but I love it and see no big difference than sleeping in a full sized room.', "It's cozy, quiet, private, and has been cost effective.", "He's mostly been working from home since covid hit, but, will be working in an office again in another state sometime soon.", 'He is waiting at least a few months for me to find another place before he moves.', 'I may need to rent out a full room but if I can find another good living situation before then, I would rather do that.', "I'm in my early 30's, like to hike and jog the trails around Gaines ranch loop, though it's a little further to get to from here.", 'I like to study and keep to myself for now.', 'I had a busy life surrounded by lots of people in the past, so want to take time off to be a little more introverted until I become extroverted again.', 'Started taking work outs seriously, study college, certifications, and various online courses.', 'Trying to learn new languages.', 'Yoga, meditation, art, video gaming on my phone, and other activities.', 'I am an apprentice electrician by trade with a few years of experience wiring houses from start to finish.', 'Have an office assistant certification and many others, and more to come.', 'Love to doordash, Instacart, Ubereats, instawork, and do a bunch of random gigs.', "Always pay rent on time, keep clean, quiet, I don't do any drugs but am 420 friendly if you are, but no hard drugs!", 'I drink a few beers a month, if that, on the trails, but am willing to not drink at all.', 'I enjoy wholesomeness.', 'I prefer someone who is peaceful, no yelling or verbal abuse.', 'No drama who likes to also keep to themselves while at home.', "I'm open to rationally talking out any potential issues with problem solving in mind, though I don't create issues.", "Possibly could help with chores, pets ect depending on the situation, in which case I wouldn't need to be introverted.", 'I was a full-time caretaker for my grandfather for a year before he passed away in 2018.', "I'm open to being in a house, condo, apt, ect.", 'Maybe you have a one bedroom or more and like the idea of renting out a walk in closet to an open minded peaceful person.', 'Send me an email, I can also send my number.', 'Thanks for reading take care.', "TLDR: Calm guy who keeps to himself looking to rent out your closet if you don't do hard drugs and aren't toxic.", 'Si hablo un poco de Espanol.']

posting_body: ['This over sized and newly updated 1 bedroom suite has tons of natural light.', 'High VAULTED ceilings, new granite counter tops.', 'The soft closing cabinets flows beautifully with the ceramic tile.', 'Samsung stainless steel appliances refrigerator, stove and dishwasher.', 'Flawless refinished hardwood floors cover the rest of the suite along with fresh paint.', 'This suite has the best bathroom in town with new ceramic tile wrapping the walls and floor in the bathroom.', 'The vanity, medicine cabinet, and even the toilet paper holder is new!', 'The suite gets a ton a naturally light and FREE heat water and sewer.', 'Newer windows!', 'You will also be surrounded with several diverse restaurants, you will have you pick of Hungarian, Japanese, French, Seafood and Soul food, Cuisine, Pizza, Coffee Shop, Movie theater, Grocery Store and so much more!', 'Transportation has never been easier with the RTA rapid that runs, through Shaker Square to Downtown, Cleveland State, Cleveland Clinic, University Hospital, JACK Casino, Rock-N-Roll hall of fame, Airport and many other popular places.']

posting_body: ['Columbus Park Apartments provides an affordable selection of Spacious 1, 2, & 3 bedroom apartments tucked away in Bedford Heights, Ohio.', 'Life at Columbus Park Apartments is carefree and convenient.', 'Our landscaped grounds offer plenty of options for you, your family, and your pets to enjoy the fresh air.', 'We offer several convenient parking options such as detached garages and covered parking.', 'We are proud to be one of the few, and best, pet-friendly apartments in the Bedford Heights area.', 'Take your furry friends to our fenced-in Bark Park so they can run around and socialize with other residents.', 'Having a safe and secure playground for your pets is just one of the many convenient amenities we offer.', 'View our full list of apartment amenities and see why our residents love living here.', 'Our community location is set back in a cul-de-sac near Tinker’s Creek.', 'You can also look forward to the many enjoyable attractions that make living at Columbus Park the place to be such as Bedford City School District, close proximity to the Bedford Reservation and Jack Thistledown Racino, as well as several shops and dining in Historic Downtown Bedford.', '-Quiet Cul-De-Sac Location', '-On-Site Management', '-Wooded Surroundings', '-Additional Storage', '-Private Balcony', '-Refrigerator', '-Online Rental Payments', '-Fenced-In Dog Park', '-Mini and Vertical Blinds', '-Covered Parking', '-Playground', '-1, 2 & 3 Bedroom Apartments', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday-Friday: 09:00 AM-06:00 PM', 'Saturday: 10:00 AM-03:00 PM', '5999 Bear Creek Drive, Bedford Heights, OH 44146', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

title: Loft apartment off downtown Clevleand
posting_body: ['This is a newly constructed UNFURNISHED loft on the second floor with a separate private entrance.', 'Located at 4533 Payne Avenue, Cleveland, Ohio, half way between downtown Cleveland and the Cleveland Clinic/CASE University.', 'All new appliances and in fact all new construction just completed in June, 2017.', '1,700 sq ft. and a 250 sq ft deck with year round grill (gas fired) right off the bedroom.', 'Open space with eight over head skylights set in a twelve foot high ceiling provides a glorious light that is enhanced with full, natural oak floors.', 'There are no buildings of comparable height within a block of the complex which allows for even more natural light and an additional feeling of openness.', 'It overlooks a large sculpture garden and has a 250 sq.ft.', 'deck in the rear which is right off the bedroom.', 'Very large bedroom which includes a walk-in closet with ample cabinets and storage space.', 'One bathroom with large walk-in shower and more cabinets for linens and storage.', 'The bathroom holds a full sized stacked washer and dryer.', 'There is an office between the kitchen and bathroom that could be a second bedroom.', 'It has a builtin desk work area; the backside of the free standing closet.', 'The openness of the space allows for almost any configuration.', 'Heat is a European wall furnace with wall mounted Italians radiators that utilize forced hot water and hot water on demand.', 'This is supplemented with an LG mini split system that supplies added heat during the cold months and provides AC during the summer months.', 'The kitchen includes maple cabinets with stained glass doors on the uppers.', 'All new stainless appliances to include gas cooktop, builtin oven and microwave, double bowl stainless sink with commercial disposal.', 'Black granite countertops that includes an additional informal dinning area on the island.', 'A separate dinning area on one side of the front space and an adjacent living/recreational area on other side.', 'Internet access and/or cable TV is offered by either Spectrum or ATT (fiber has been installed) which are tenants responsibility.', "The loft has it's own security system that includes an outdoor perimeter.", 'Large secure off street parking with room for two cars and key fob controlled auto gate.', 'This area is extremely safe as it has become incorporated into the outer boundary of Cleveland State  and Asiatown.', 'The side streets are single family homes and the main streets a mix of residential/light industrial.', "Once a thriving part of Cleveland's gilded past it is, as is the rest of the city, transiting to a service economy.", 'Think the Cleveland Clinic, CASE University and the emerging urban campus of Cleveland State University.', 'Going down Payne towards downtown Cleveland one Asian restaurant (and Asian market) after the other beckons you to fabulous cooking with heartfelt service.', "New Dave's located conveniently at Chester and 57th Street.", 'There is a separate very secure, private entrance way.', '.', '$1900/month plus utilities.', 'Security deposit (one months rent).', 'Credit check, references and pet security deposit required.', ' Available 01 August 2022.']

posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; posting_body: ['Columbus Park Apartments provides an affordable selection of Spacious 1, 2, & 3 bedroom apartments tucked away in Bedford Heights, Ohio.', 'Life at Columbus Park Apartments is carefree and convenient.', 'Our landscaped grounds offer plenty of options for you, your family, and your pets to enjoy the fresh air.', 'We offer several convenient parking options such as detached garages and covered parking.', 'We are proud to be one of the few, and best, pet-friendly apartments in the Bedford Heights area.', 'Take your furry friends to our fenced-in Bark Park so they can run around and socialize with other residents.', 'Having a safe and secure playground for your pets is just one of the many convenient amenities we offer.', 'View our full list of apartment amenities and see why our residents love living here.', 'Our community location is set back in a cul-de-sac near Tinker’s Creek.', 'You can also look forward to the many enjoyable attractions that make living at Columbus Park the place to be such as Bedford City School District, close proximity to the Bedford Reservation and Jack Thistledown Racino, as well as several shops and dining in Historic Downtown Bedford.', '-Additional Storage', '-Fenced-In Dog Park', '-On-Site Laundry Facilities', '-Quiet Cul-De-Sac Location', '-Private Balcony', '-On-Site Management', '-Gas Range', '-1, 2 & 3 Bedroom Apartments', '-Covered Parking', '-Central Air Conditioning', '-Mini and Vertical Blinds', '-Detached Garages', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday-Friday: 09:00 AM-06:00 PM', 'Saturday: 10:00 AM-03:00 PM', '5999 Bear Creek Drive, Bedford Heights, OH 44146', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']

posting_body: ['ROCKPORT VILLAGE', '3209 Rocky River Drive', 'Cleveland, Ohio 44111', 'show contact info', 'BEN | North Coast Capital Partners |', 'show contact info', '3209 Rocky River Drive | Townhome | $1,299/month | Bedrooms: 3 | Bathrooms: 1 |  Sq Footage: 1,300 |  Parking: 1 Garage | Pet Policy: No Pets |  Security Deposit: $1,299', 'DESCRIPTION:', "Living in Cleveland, Ohio doesn't get any better than Rockport Village!!", ' Conveniently located in beautiful Westpark across from the Metroparks and St. Joseph Academy, Rockport Village offers spacious two and three bedroom individual homes, town homes and apartments, all with the feel of owning your own home with all the conveniences of leasing.', ' With the Metroparks across the street running, hiking, walking, biking and golfing are right outside your front door.', ' In the Metroparks you will find access to Lake Erie for boating, fishing, canoeing, kayaking and area beaches.', ' At home enjoy the beautifully landscaped private grounds.', 'Shopping, transportation, dining, and entertainment are all within reach.', 'Rockport Village is located just minutes from downtown Cleveland with easy access to major highways I-90, I-71 and I-480 and the Ohio Turnpike.', 'Hopkins International Airport, Fairview Park Hospital and Kamms Corner are just a short drive away.', "For those who don't drive public transportation awaits you out your front door.", "If you're looking for apartments, town houses or single family houses for rent in Westpark, Cleveland or the west side make Rockport Village your choice.", 'RENTAL FEATURES:', 'Central Heat- Fireplace- Refrigerator- Oven / Range- Basement Storage- Washer- Dryer- High-Speed Internet / Cable Ready', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES:', 'Garage Parking (1)- Courtyard', 'CONTACT:', 'BEN | North Coast Capital Partners |', 'show contact info']

posting_body: ['Courtland Ave,  Welcome to 13509 Courtland Avenue; a charming and delightful 3 bedroom bungalow that has been well maintained & cared for over the years.', "As you enter the front door with stained glass panels, you're invited into the bright and open Living Room with newer carpet.", 'From there you will find the large Eat-In kitchen with white wood cabinetry, formica countertops, and ceramic tile backsplash.', 'A great view of the beautiful backyard is offered from this room.', 'Two spacious Bedrooms with hardwood floors can be found on the main floor as well as an updated full bathroom with ceramic tile floor & convenient tub / shower combination.', 'The spacious Primary Bedroom comprises the entire second floor and features wood paneled walls and newer carpet.', 'There is plenty of closet & storage space available on the second floor including built in shelves and an oversized cedar closet to meet your needs.', 'The partially Finished Basement offers additional living space with a sizable recreation room for your enjoyment with newer carpet and glass block windows.', 'There is also a half bath located on the lower level.', 'This home also features a fully fenced in backyard, a wonderful place to enjoy some time outdoors, and a 1 car detached garage with additional storage space.', "Located near the Kamm's Corners neighborhood with close proximity to the Metroparks & quick interstate access.", 'Easy commute to Downtown Cleveland & beyond.', "Don't miss the opportunity to see all that this special home has to offer!"]

posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school;
