posting_body: ["An investors' special with great income potential!!", 'Located in the heart of Sunnyvale, this Duplex features a 3bed/2 bath main home and a completely remodeled 2bed/1bath ADU.', 'Both units feature new paint, hardwood flooring, throughout, a nicely landscaped front yard.', 'The main house features a large kitchen with partial new cabinets and countertops, new sink, sink disposer, and a dishwasher.', 'A huge potential for investors to finish the huge basement for additional rent.', 'The ADU features 2beds/1 bath, kitchen and living room with new paint, new laminate flooring, new lighting fixtures, new doors and new baseboards.', 'kitchen with new dishwasher, sink with disposer, hood, new cabinets and countertops, remodeled bathroom and a new roof.', 'The Front yard is tastefully landscaped.', 'Plenty of parking space!', 'Located close to Hi-tech companies, shopping, trendy restaurants and bars, Caltrain station, freeways, SJ Airport, golf course and a lot more.', "Don't miss the Farmers."]

title: BEWARE Postings to this address are a SCAM
posting_body: ['I responded to a post to rent the downstairs unit of 1230 W 5th St in Lorain.', 'After a days worth of back and forth texts to get a few basic questions answered, I was asked to send $50 via Zelle or Cash App and once the person verified funds were received I would THEN be sent the Application to complete.', 'There was a point when I was trying to get verification on if WiFi was included or if there was a TV, that the person responding went MIA.', 'I waited about 30 min, the being cautious by nature, I decided to use a public record search to see if I could verify who owned the property.', 'I was not only able to do that, but as they use a mobile phone for their business, it was available online.', 'I contacted the owner, sent a copy of the post and was told THEN that it was NOT put up by their property management group.', '2 hours later I heard back from the person who I had been communicating with.', 'I had not yet received contact info for the Prop Mgt Co from the owner.', 'I asked this person multi questions in hopes I would be wrong and they were just a representative.', 'Once they said they were the owner, then asked for the $ o knew it was a scam.', 'When I sent them a screenshot from the Lorain County Assessor Site as well as one showing the actual Owners name they had the audacity to tell my that THEY owned the bottom of the house and this person I found owned the top !!!', 'I flagged the posts which they placed in multiple categories and within 24 hours they reposted them.', 'ATTENTION: despite their ad being flagged.', 'The Craigslist program allowed them to repost the original listing.', 'It’s currently double posted in 2 categories and Craigslist chooses not to provide any way for me to give them the reason for my flagging the post OR give them the info I have from the poster.']

title: Electronic Thermostat, Historic Building, BBQ/Picnic Area
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; title: House with dock, in Lagoons
posting_body: ['Small, luxurious 2 bedroom home located in the beautiful Mentor Lagoons harbor available August 1st.', ' All major appliances, air conditioning, 2 car garage, and convenient water access that includes a 30 foot steel dock and a jet-ski dock.', 'Inside enjoy the 1700 square feet of wood paneled open-format living space with a single bedroom upstairs (with full bath including a shower) and a single bedroom downstairs (with a full bath including an oversize whirlpool tub).', '  An upper and lower deck in the back of the house both look out over the docks and the harbor channel.', ' Privately set back from the road, you can come home from work, jump in your boat, and be on Lake Erie after just a ten minute cruise up the channel.']

title: BBQ/Picnic Area, Rhino Security Deposit Option, Flex Rent Payments
posting_body: ["Once Ohio's largest high school, now one of Cleveland's most innovative apartment communities, The Brick Lofts at Historic West Tech High is a must see.", 'It is a beautiful building with exceptional architecture and construction qualities, unique loft-style apartment floor plans, and superior amenities.', 'Come experience the new stylish, and sophisticated look of the former West Tech High School.', 'Beautifully planned suites with a variety of 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment floor plans are available for you to call home.', 'You will find yourself living a lifestyle that fits your needs.', 'Constructed in 1912, the $32 million conversion of the West Tech High School into the West Tech Lofts in 2003- 2004, preserved the architecture, charm and character of the school; even the lockers adorn the corridors.', 'Superior and modern amenities in both the common areas and the private residences, compliment this one of a kind renovation.', 'Outstanding community amenities include garage parking, an exceptional fitness center, spacious game room, laundry center, and a community room created from the original high school auditorium, and off-street or garage parking.', "Just seconds from the I-90 freeway and just minutes from Downtown Cleveland, Lakewood, Ohio City and Tremont; title: 2 bedroom 2 bath Carlyle on The Lake
posting_body: ['Available for Rent Sept 1, 2022     Lovely, recently redecorated 2 bedroom 2 bath suite in much desired Carlyle on the Lake.', 'The Carlyle recently underwent a 5.5 million dollar renovation and is one of the most desired buildings on the lake front.', "The available unit's recent upgrades include carpeting, window treatments, new paint, kitchen appliances and counter-tops, bathroom flooring and vanities.", 'The apartment is in pristine condition and offers fabulous sunset views over the wooded lakeside Lakewood area from your private balcony.', 'The large master bedroom has a large walk-in closet and en-suite bath.', 'One heated, underground garage space included and one storage locker.', '24 hour reception/security, indoor/outdoor pools, beach access, sauna, jacuzzi, fitness center, billiards room with jukebox, two party rooms, conference room, guest suite, Summerhouse Restaurant, deli, hair and barber salon, real estate office, and more!', 'Tenant occupied through July 31.', 'The Carlyle is considered to have the best amenities on the Gold Coast.', 'The monthly rental is $1,700']
